The paper focuses on object recognition with deep convolutional neural networks, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the evolution of network architectures, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the usage of neural networks for image data generation, which is a topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
